INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES("1504", "187", "content_body", "Waterfalls hidden away by jungle and rice terraced mountains, they exist beyond the post cards- they exist in Lombok. This largely untouched Indonesian island is home to some of the best diving in the world, white-sand beaches and the secluded, Seven Secrets Resort. As the only resort located on the shores of the Nipah Bay, Seven Secrets doesn’t take its role as your ambassador to the Indonesian tropics lightly. located just east of Bali in Indonesia. Explore these lush, exquisite white-sand beaches full away from it all on your very private paradise. This 6 star luxury retreat is a secret escape blended with local architecture and contemporary style. It’s tropical surrounding creates an unforgettable experience for old and new travelers alike, due to a culture of personalized service and culinary masterpieces.\r\n\r\n<b>Why Seven Secrets?</b>\r\n\r\nWhile seemingly withholding seven, it is no secret that life really is all about balance. The resort is committed to sharing their secrets in order to get your body, mind and spirit back into balance. If you’ve ever felt run down and in need of a reset button on life, Seven Secrets is the getaway that will help realign your sense of self and well being without the distractions. From the immediate massage and complimentary cocktail at check-in, to the aromatherapy utilized suites, guests are not only treated to a resort but to an all inclusive wellness retreat. Equipped with a Michelin Star chef, a world champion molecular mixologist, and a staff trained in Asian and European therapies, you will be rejuvenated from the inside out. And, with only 24 suites, the staff has its resources and focus aimed directly towards your needs.\r\n\r\n<b>Accommodation </b>\r\n\r\nSeven Secrets knows that well-being stems largely from our surroundings and they take every detail of their suites into consideration. With a mix of Indonesian architecture and handicraft art, each suite is carefully designed to be simple, modern and organic. Guests are afforded the feeling of a remote, southeast Asian jungle stay with all of the amenities of the modern world. The resort will assign a personal butler to deliver breakfast right to your room and evenings can be spent in the suite’s terrace Jacuzzi, drinking wine from your own personal cellar while taking in the ocean views.\r\n\r\n<b>Make it Extra Special </b>\r\n\r\nGuests will enjoy the breathtaking views of green hillsides and beautiful mountains with the salty sweet smell of the Indian Ocean. Lombok Island genuinely hits every traveler’s wish and sparkles like a true gem. For the experience of a true wellness retreat, come balance out your body and mind by indulging in the healing procedures of the Seven Secret’s spa. With the creation of a private oasis featuring the soothing scents, sights and sounds of nature, you may partake in massages, facials, detoxifying diets, stress reduction therapies and harmony centered couples therapies. Once physically and mentally balanced, enjoy the concierge itineraries that will have you yachting, diving or taking helicopter tours to the nearby Gili Islands, Bali or the Gunung Rinjani volcano.\r\n\r\nLet Seven Secrets nurture the nature in you through the inspiration of the nature that lies on its very doorstep. This bucket list experience is a sophisticated beauty and unlike any other in the world. Visit 7 Secrets Resort and discover your hidden secret today.\r\n\r\n<b>Other Indonesian options</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Take an extended trip to Bali</li>\r\n	<li>Sip Copi Lukak or Sumatran Coffee daily!</li>\r\n	<li>Explore Sanur’s beaches, Ubud’s rice terraces, monkey forest and temples,</li>\r\n	<li>Hike at nighttime for a not to be missed sunrise Volcano experience.</li>\r\n	<li>Visit Gili Islands and Ahmed for some of the best diving spots on the planet.</li>\r\n</ul>");
