INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("246", "1", "2015-09-09 23:24:00", "2015-09-09 23:24:00", "Offering the most exclusive and behind the scenes experiences in the game, we introduce to you, Blaycation Poker.\r\n\r\nHelping our guests from around the globe check off their bucket lists is our primary objective.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>Bucket lists are usually associated with travel, adrenalin activities and major sporting events. <span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>At Blaycation Poker, we specialize in providing Bucket List Poker Vacations for you, The Poker Player.\r\n\r\nImagine sitting under the bright lights, playing live poker against famous pros at a major poker event. Feel like you may buckle under the pressure? Fell like you are a little overwhelmed? With Blaycation Poker, you won’t be just thrown to the wolves. Throughout the experience, you will be accompanied by a professional poker player, who will stay in your corner to strategize, teach and mentor you the entire way through.\r\n\r\nExperienced in fulfilling the dreams of Poker enthusiasts all over the world, we offer a fully interactive and comprehensive Poker vacation that you can’t experience anywhere else.\r\n\r\n<b>Previous Blaycation Poker experiences have included the following:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Major Poker tournament</li>\r\n	<li>VIP Welcome</li>\r\n	<li>Hotel accommodations</li>\r\n	<li>Welcome dinner and cocktails</li>\r\n	<li>Private training seminar</li>\r\n	<li>Official tour of poker event</li>\r\n	<li>Poker Pro appearances</li>\r\n	<li>Individual coaching and mentoring</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-tournament strategy breakfast</li>\r\n	<li>Exclusive private concierge service</li>\r\n	<li>Poker Pro logoed clothing</li>\r\n	<li>Welcome and Farewell gift</li>\r\n	<li>Memories for a Lifetime</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWith the goal of having a trip of a lifetime in mind, we take care of all the technicalities for you so that you can focus on playing your most successful game yet.\r\n\r\nTrusted Poker pro and media personality, Bernard Lee is at the forefront of the Blaycation Poker experience, ready to show you the ropes. Regularly called ‘The Hardest Working Man in Poker,” Lee is prepared to share with you all of his knowledge and expertise that will leave you with an unforgettable Blaycation Poker experience.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-238\" src=\"//localhost:3000/blaycation/bower_components/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/bernard-lee_blaycation-poker-1000x1000.jpeg\" alt=\"bernard-lee_blaycation-poker\" width=\"680\" height=\"680\" />\r\n\r\nBernard Lee, Blaycation’s official Spokesperson, catapulted into the poker spotlight after he finished 13th in the 2005 World Series of Poker (WSOP) Main Event. Lee, a former marketing professional, has amassed over $2.1 million in career winnings and captured six tournament titles on the poker tournament circuit.\r\n\r\nAway from the tables, Lee is one of the busiest poker media personalities in the business. Lee is the co-host of ESPN Inside Deal, poker columnist for Boston Herald, ESPN.com and Card Player magazine, radio host of \"The Bernard Lee Poker Show\" and has previously commentated for the WSOP and the Eastern Poker Tour. Lee has also been an instructor for World Poker Tour Boot Camp, World Series of Poker Academy and has taught hundreds of private students. He is RunGoodGear Pro &amp; Blue Shark Optic team Pro. Educated in the New England area (Harvard University, B.A., M.A.; Babson College M.B.A.), he currently lives in the Boston area with his wife and two kids.\r\n\r\nHis interpersonal skills, coupled with his teaching style and his deep industry relationships inside and out of the poker world gives our clients a refreshing and completely interactive snapshot into the poker world in a highly entertaining and informative way.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-239\" src=\"//localhost:3000/blaycation/bower_components/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Blaycation-Poker-5.png\" alt=\"The Blaycation Poker Team\" width=\"660\" height=\"438\" />\r\n\r\nIn short, Blaycation has you covered from the moment you arrive to the last hand you play.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>Each trip is designed slightly differently, but in the end, you will have a poker trip that you will remember forever!<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>And if you play your cards right you might just go home with more than just amazing new friends and memories.\r\n\r\n<b>Here are what a few of our happy clients had to say:</b>\r\n\r\n<em>\"My Blaycation bucket list at the WSOP 2015 was one of my greatest events ever attended, Mark and Bernard were exceptional hosts, highly recommend.\"</em>\r\n\r\n- Gerry McWeeney Los Angeles\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>“These guys know how to tick off your bucket lists. I got to go on the main stage and hold a WSOP bracelet and they framed the picture for me. Are you kidding me? This trip was more than I ever could have imagined!”<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span></em>\r\n\r\n- Warren from Boston\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>“What an amazing poker experience. I have played in my home game for years and always dreamed of playing live at a big event like the WSOP and finally it’s a reality.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>Blaycation made the experience even more incredible.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>I’m looking forward to my next Blaycation Poker Trip.”</em>\r\n\r\n- Kempton form Louisiana\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>“I got to meet three WSOP world champions and participate in an interview with one of my heroes too. I can take home more than just memories from this experience. I can’t thank you enough.” </em>\r\n\r\n- Jason from Minnesota.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>“Both my wife and I are big poker players and we were just blown away with this Blaycation experience. Not only did I meet my hero and get a picture and autograph from him (Barry Greenstein) but Cindy got a big hug from her favorite Daniel Negreanu too.”</em>\r\n\r\n- Mike &amp; Cindy Bolster Idaho\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>“The personal and genuine interest that Bernard and Mark took in me and my game play made this experience unforgettable. Not to mention I got to meet and talk with my favorite poker player, Jason Mercier.”</em>\r\n\r\n- Kurt from Colorado\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>\"First class organization!<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>We were treated like royalty and had insider access to areas at the World Series of Poker we never could have dreamed of having!\" </em>\r\n\r\n- Chad and Tammy Christian\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>“Having a sit down with Norman Chad to shoot the breeze was a major unexpected surprise for me. He’s a funny, caring and a terrific guy. Thanks Bernard.”</em>\r\n\r\n- EW from Mexico\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>“Had I not received personal one-on-one coaching from Bernard, I would not have run so deep. I will be back again and again and I’m brining all my mates.”</em>\r\n\r\n- Brett from Cincinnati.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-240\" src=\"//localhost:3000/blaycation/bower_components/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/image4.jpg\" alt=\"image4\" width=\"696\" height=\"293\" />\r\n\r\nWe also offer a specialized service for existing poker groups and leagues wanting to make their experience extra special. Please contact us for full details.\r\n\r\nHere is our latest Poker Experience.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blaycation.com/destinations/north-america/ultimate-poker-trip/\">http://blaycation.com/destinations/north-america/ultimate-poker-trip/</a>\r\n\r\nWe have a variety of authorized poker Satellite locations all over North America where you can play for a chance to experience one of our Bucket List Poker Blaycations.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to know more please contact <a href=\"mailto:Mark@blaycation.com\">Mark@blaycation.com</a> or <a href=\"mailto:Bernard@blaycation.com\">Bernard@blaycation.com</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Blaycation Poker In The Press</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pokernews.com/news/2015/03/bernard-lee-blaycation-21089.htm\">Bernard Lee Signs as Spokesperson with Blaycation</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pokernews.com/news/2015/05/colossal-experience-check-off-blaycation-bucket-list-21688.htm\">A Colossal Experience: A Check Off the Blaycation Bucket List</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y3dxlv6L6HA\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y3dxlv6L6HA</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blaycation.com/destinations/north-america/wsop-lucky777/\">http://blaycation.com/destinations/north-america/wsop-lucky777/</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<iframe style=\"width:100%;min-height:450px\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jyaySQ5P1Ls\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;", "Poker", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "231-revision-v1", "", "", "2015-09-09 23:24:00", "2015-09-09 23:24:00", "", "231", "http://localhost/blaycation/bower_components/wordpress/231-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
