If you would like to know more please contact <a href=\"mailto:Mark@blaycation.com\">Mark@blaycation.com</a> or <a href=\"mailto:Bernard@blaycation.com\">Bernard@blaycation.com</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Blaycation Poker In The Press</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pokernews.com/news/2015/03/bernard-lee-blaycation-21089.htm\">Bernard Lee Signs as Spokesperson with Blaycation</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pokernews.com/news/2015/05/colossal-experience-check-off-blaycation-bucket-list-21688.htm\">A Colossal Experience: A Check Off the Blaycation Bucket List</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y3dxlv6L6HA\">Colossus is on Warren\'s bucket list, is it on yours?</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UdEIGYnNlXI\">Checking Off the World Series of Poker from the Bucket List</a>\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;", "Poker", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "231-revision-v1", "", "", "2015-09-09 23:28:24", "2015-09-09 23:28:24", "", "231", "http://localhost/blaycation/bower_components/wordpress/231-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("251", "1", "2015-09-09 23:31:23", "2015-09-09 23:31:23", "We believe Incentive-based travel must go way beyond the norm. It needs to be personal, accessible and highly memorable. Our approach to creating and executing incentive travel programs is to promise, and deliver, once-in-a-lifetime experiences to corporations and their teams. We’ll elevate your brand image on your trip and take it from ‘average perk’ to an ‘absolute winner.’\r\n\r\n<b>Our Approach</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We believe in partnering with our clients from the beginning to design the perfect travel programs.</li>\r\n	<li>We secure the best locations and deliver a most memorable experience for everyone.</li>\r\n	<li>We make the pre-program journey just as enjoyable as the destination itself.</li>\r\n	<li>We provide a stress-free, collaborative and engaging process, keeping you totally informed so there are no surprises.</li>\r\n	<li>We bring your people together in the most <i>effective</i> way for your business. To showcase and reward them.</li>\r\n	<li>We create the best <i>experiences</i> for the greatest number of guests, while maximizing your budget.</li>\r\n	<li>Our goal is to make each one of your guests feel proud, fulfilled, inspired and special, even though they are part of a larger group.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>About Us</b>\r\n\r\nLike our name suggests, Blaycation designs and curates custom bucket list vacation experiences for our clients. We provide unique and tailored Meeting and Incentive Travel Solutions for businesses and we know their success comes from highly motivated employees.\r\n\r\nOur Incentive Travel programs allows you to <i>focus your message</i> toward your top performers and your best customers while they are away from their daily lives. We know that best results come from these achievers feeling proud, celebrated, inspired and relaxed. Providing you a winning formula and great <i>investment</i> into the future of your company.\r\n\r\nWe provide a <i>simple approach</i> for the organizer and a <i>rewards experience</i> for the guest – <i>with exceptional value </i>to maximize your budget.\r\n\r\nWith our worldwide travel network and experiences, precision planning, incredible service and many enticing all-inclusive &amp; exclusive destinations to choose from, we’ll make the whole experience easy and very rewarding.\r\n\r\n<b>Our Products &amp; Services</b>\r\n\r\nAt Blaycation, we create custom programs for our clients by sourcing incredibly well matched destinations and hotel properties that offer an “all-inclusive” experience including meals, beverages, accommodations, etc. Plus we create well matched excursions and team building programs to “fit” your individualized corporate style. We also offer a VIP and Executive Bucket-List Service too.\r\n\r\nOur in-house team with over 30+ years of combined <i>travel and incentive experience</i> is absolutely ready to make your event run as smooth as possible, with:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Worldwide travel knowledge and expertise</li>\r\n	<li>A creative &amp; communicative process.</li>\r\n	<li>A carefully planned trip designed to maximize participation.</li>\r\n	<li>Expert supplier negotiations and budget management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nA Blaycation experience will leave your participants feeling rewarded, happy and inspired. Your people will be looked after from start to finish, with no detail left unattended.\r\n\r\nFrom intimate executive retreats to corporate getaways and national sales meetings, Blaycation’s strategic and fresh creativity will help bring your meetings and events to a whole new level.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-262\" src=\"//localhost:3000/blaycation/bower_components/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/ptf6-1024x573.jpg\" alt=\"Blaycation Corporate Retreat\" width=\"1024\" height=\"573\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Why Corporate Getaways &amp; Incentives?</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Research has proven that high employee engagement equates to higher productivity.</li>\r\n	<li>When you build a culture that your people can believe in you get results.</li>\r\n	<li>Designing the absolute best employee appreciation events that reflect and celebrate your corporate culture motivate your employees</li>\r\n	<li>Happy, incentivized and motivated employees results in better bottom lines</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Our Services</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hotel sourcing, negotiating, and contracting</li>\r\n	<li>Finding the perfect sporting event or location to motivate your employees</li>\r\n	<li>Registration</li>\r\n	<li>End to end transportation management</li>\r\n	<li>Attendee and VIP management</li>\r\n	<li>Analysis of budget variance</li>\r\n	<li>Total logistical management</li>\r\n	<li>Planning and management of all receptions, group activities and optional tours</li>\r\n	<li>Planning and management of all, sports celebrity, entertainment and décor elements</li>\r\n	<li>Create and manage all food and beverage</li>\r\n	<li>Complete on-site program management</li>\r\n	<li>VIP &amp; Concierge &amp; Bucket List Services</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-tour selection services</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Whether your team is rewarded with a major sporting event, private Island get away or exotic all-inclusive destination, we make sure your corporation is front and center throughout the whole program. We deliver a premium Blaycation service from start to finish.</em>\r\n\r\n<b>To speak to us about designing a Corporate Getaway or Corporate Retreat, Please call us for more information <a href=\"tel:+19024415664\">+19024415664</a> </b>\r\n\r\nMark Stiles, <em>President &amp; Chief Vacation Officer</em>", "Corporate Getaways", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "blaycation-corporate-getaways", "", "", "2015-09-10 00:01:49", "2015-09-10 00:01:49", "", "0", "http://localhost/blaycation/bower_components/wordpress/?page_id=251", "0", "page", "", "0");
